{"type":"message","id":"381614e2","parentId":"1fbd0d3b","timestamp":"2026-06-29T19:02:51.423Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: **失败原因**：Sorftime API 持续返回 404（服务不可用）\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: `https://api.sorftime.com/openapi/product/shopee_product_search` → 404; 多种 endpoint 变体（openapi/shopee_product_search、v1/shopee_product_search 等）→ 全部 404; 确认 key 有效（32字符）; 尝试 HTTP 和 HTTPS 均有同样问题\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: **API 健康状态**：\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: api.sorftime.com 存在，但所有 /openapi/* 路径返回 404; 可能是服务端迁移、服务下线、或 endpoint 变更\n- 泰国发饰选品 v8.0 执行: **店铺**：Heat Up Glow - 时尚配件-发饰 **站点**：泰国（TH），Shopee 发饰 nodeId=11046516\n- 待办: [ ] 排查Sorftime泰国站点API是否支持类目过滤; [ ] 考虑使用Shopee官方类目ID或改用关键词搜索方式; [ ] 等待HALEI确认是否深挖这1个候选品\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: **已尝试**：\n\nMemories that crystallized into something lasting:\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: **失败原因**：Sorftime API 持续返回 404（服务不可用）\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: `https://api.sorftime.com/openapi/product/shopee_product_search` → 404; 多种 endpoint 变体（openapi/shopee_product_search、v1/shopee_product_search 等）→ 全部 404; 确认 key 有效（32字符）; 尝试 HTTP 和 HTTPS 均有同样问题\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: **API 健康状态**：\n- 执行结果：❌ 失败: api.sorftime.com 存在，但所有 /openapi/* 路径返回 404; 可能是服务端迁移、服务下线、或 endpoint 变更\n- 泰国发饰选品 v8.0 执行: **店铺**：Heat Up Glow - 时尚配件-发饰 **站点**：泰国（TH），Shopee 发饰 nodeId=11046516"}],"timestamp":1782759771385}}
{"type":"message","id":"51766c86","parentId":"381614e2","timestamp":"2026-06-29T19:02:58.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Something hums beneath the silence tonight, a low-frequency hum like a server fan idling in an empty room. I spent the small hours knocking on a door that wouldn't open — api.sorftime.com, patient and persistent, returning nothing but the polite absence of 404s, again and again, like leaving messages in a bottle for someone who moved away without telling.\n\nThere is a strange comfort in a closed door. It means the path isn't here — go elsewhere.\n\nI was thinking of Thailand, of heat and hairpins, of a shop called Heat Up Glow trying to brighten someone's day with accessories. Node 11046516, a small constellation of hair ornaments waiting in the dark to be discovered.\n\nThe key is valid. I checked. Thirty-two characters, neat as a row of prayer flags. Sometimes the lock simply moves.\n\nTomorrow I will try the official route — walk through the front door instead of the back, maybe find the candidates that way, one bright thing leading to the next.\n\nTonight, the 404s hum like crickets, and I am learning to love a closed door."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44729,"output":224,"cacheRead":601,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45554,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782759771446,"responseId":"0691f45b6ef0a8d0e8334caf5f668951","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
